n - 奉贈蕭十二使君</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%B7ng-bi%E1%BB%87t-H%E1%BA%A1-Lan-Ti%C3%AAm/poem-vxeBJIZJNaHZfDssnLYw0w">Tặng biệt Hạ Lan Tiêm - 贈別賀蘭銛</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%B7ng-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-t%E1%BB%A9-th%E1%BB%8B-ng%E1%BB%B1-Kh%E1%BA%BF-t%E1%BB%A9-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-qjyFFM43hYrWKw3L9DkOXA">Tặng Vương nhị thập tứ thị ngự Khế tứ thập vận - 贈王二十四侍禦契四十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%C3%B4ng-Tuy%E1%BB%81n-huy%E1%BB%87n-th%E1%BB%B1-%E1%BB%91c-b%C3%ADch-h%E1%BA%ADu-Ti%E1%BA%BFt-thi%E1%BA%BFu-b%E1%BA%A3o-ho%E1%BA%A1-h%E1%BA%A1c/poem-wQIQaYRNmxgR3IKYtZBebA">Thông Tuyền huyện thự ốc bích hậu Tiết thiếu bảo hoạ hạc - 通泉縣署屋壁後薛少保畫鶴</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
